{"id": "ChIJnQsVUDjGwoARcEGiOJrPzZY", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 1799, "displayName": {"text": "Sushi Gen", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Locals line up at this simple sushi bar, known for traditional Japanese preparations & lunch deals.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJnQsVUDjGwoARcEGiOJrPzZY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSeVpXODRZa2REY25nMlNrSlVORlZQU2sxdWNIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Sushi Gen is my absolute favorite Japanese sushi restaurant. If you’re craving sashimi or sushi, this is the place to visit — you’ll enjoy some of the freshest and most satisfying quality fish around.\n\nThis place is always crowded. Lunch, dinner, weekdays, weekends — there’s almost always a line. If you want to avoid waiting, try coming around 5 PM for dinner. That’s usually the best time to get in without a long wait.\n\nEspecially on weekends, the line gets even longer, so plan accordingly. But overall, the quality is absolutely worth it. Highly recommended.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Sushi Gen is my absolute favorite Japanese sushi restaurant. If you’re craving sashimi or sushi, this is the place to visit — you’ll enjoy some of the freshest and most satisfying quality fish around.\n\nThis place is always crowded. Lunch, dinner, weekdays, weekends — there’s almost always a line. If you want to avoid waiting, try coming around 5 PM for dinner. That’s usually the best time to get in without a long wait.\n\nEspecially on weekends, the line gets even longer, so plan accordingly. But overall, the quality is absolutely worth it. Highly recommended.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Douglas Shin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107572007472804734737/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiI-tkTAQYVhYG7XEqcEQxjAtAEy0bStWNwGj4YISzxmHE6BoUrA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-26T01:59:47.924403034Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSeVpXODRZa2REY25nMlNrSlVORlZQU2sxdWNIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSeVpXODRZa2REY25nMlNrSlVORlZQU2sxdWNIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c63850150b9d:0x96cdcf9a38a24170"}, {"name": "places/ChIJnQsVUDjGwoARcEGiOJrPzZY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twUFJWcFVRV3B0TFU5RGRscFhNRzUxVEc1d05IYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This sushi place is the best in town.\nRaw tuna has an absolutely superb taste. It’s of great quality and has a high turnover rate, ensuring that you can always enjoy fresh sushi. However, one unfortunate aspect is that we don’t take reservations, which means we have to wait for at least 20 minutes.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This sushi place is the best in town.\nRaw tuna has an absolutely superb taste. It’s of great quality and has a high turnover rate, ensuring that you can always enjoy fresh sushi. However, one unfortunate aspect is that we don’t take reservations, which means we have to wait for at least 20 minutes.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "JM", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113740474717276890843/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW71dTSr3k3ZOQeLVj-WKSsdS-882yaG7MuKWvfZnvxKCnCtw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-29T16:32:56.365458426Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twUFJWcFVRV3B0TFU5RGRscFhNRzUxVEc1d05IYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twUFJWcFVRV3B0TFU5RGRscFhNRzUxVEc1d05IYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c63850150b9d:0x96cdcf9a38a24170"}, {"name": "places/ChIJnQsVUDjGwoARcEGiOJrPzZY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tzNFNXVlZielpVTVhOM2RUY3RZamR4UjFJdFlYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The highest quality sushi in LA! Order the omakase and let the sushi masters work their magic. They'll keep giving you treats until you say no more. Price is reasonable for this level quality. When you order Amiebi you can choose the between fried head or miso soup with head.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The highest quality sushi in LA! Order the omakase and let the sushi masters work their magic. They'll keep giving you treats until you say no more. Price is reasonable for this level quality. When you order Amiebi you can choose the between fried head or miso soup with head.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jung Park", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111021009877641396947/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcqZKa5X7xj0H4Z7Tg6xn88FH7gUNnQpuzJ81Uec5Ae1t2b5R1dA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-07T02:00:25.447660156Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tzNFNXVlZielpVTVhOM2RUY3RZamR4UjFJdFlYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tzNFNXVlZielpVTVhOM2RUY3RZamR4UjFJdFlYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c63850150b9d:0x96cdcf9a38a24170"}, {"name": "places/ChIJnQsVUDjGwoARcEGiOJrPzZY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNNGNUSlhPRTVxTW5kQlIxWTFiblpXTTNOMVkyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My favorite place for sushi in LA. The quality is amazing—this is one of the only places where the tuna actually tastes fresh and truly delicious. I’ve been to countless sushi spots all over California, and nothing beats this place. A lot of other places are overpriced and don’t even come close in taste.\nIt’s not really a spot to sit and relax, mainly because they’re always busy and trying to accommodate a high volume of customers. I usually avoid places with long lines, but this is the one exception—I’m always willing to wait because it’s worth it.\nIn the beginning, I didn’t love coming here because of the service, but after meeting Ayumi, the experience has gotten much better. She’s incredibly sweet and attentive, and really makes a difference.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My favorite place for sushi in LA. The quality is amazing—this is one of the only places where the tuna actually tastes fresh and truly delicious. I’ve been to countless sushi spots all over California, and nothing beats this place. A lot of other places are overpriced and don’t even come close in taste.\nIt’s not really a spot to sit and relax, mainly because they’re always busy and trying to accommodate a high volume of customers. I usually avoid places with long lines, but this is the one exception—I’m always willing to wait because it’s worth it.\nIn the beginning, I didn’t love coming here because of the service, but after meeting Ayumi, the experience has gotten much better. She’s incredibly sweet and attentive, and really makes a difference.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "J C", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100581268421070929091/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI4WPRXHCVV0MXC9z1WKrPn21rsW3IfqFI4efN1n4m095SpQA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-13T23:20:36.885654185Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNNGNUSlhPRTVxTW5kQlIxWTFiblpXTTNOMVkyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNNGNUSlhPRTVxTW5kQlIxWTFiblpXTTNOMVkyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c63850150b9d:0x96cdcf9a38a24170"}, {"name": "places/ChIJnQsVUDjGwoARcEGiOJrPzZY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsZlRIQjZWMVJpTmtGbGNWSjNNbGRGT1hKS2JrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Truly one of the most delicious things I’ve ever eaten. I never really understood how sushi rice should be seasoned and the quality of the fish is outstanding. Splurge for the premium chirashi with bbq eel.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Truly one of the most delicious things I’ve ever eaten. I never really understood how sushi rice should be seasoned and the quality of the fish is outstanding. Splurge for the premium chirashi with bbq eel.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Marco Moliterni", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118422710515898071967/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJfhUTNs8KzNtLwjfpmnvkdL_i2yh9sgT9X77TuspEAb3k16U=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-21T14:35:46.831304768Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsZlRIQjZWMVJpTmtGbGNWSjNNbGRGT1hKS2JrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsZlRIQjZWMVJpTmtGbGNWSjNNbGRGT1hKS2JrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c63850150b9d:0x96cdcf9a38a24170"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJnQsVUDjGwoARcEGiOJrPzZY/photos/AWCwydiXMJ65FELya8Y284NB9zKn_tWUHa4h-6LWEenGMIDdEv9kkV-LoFGMtfzpmuT9mMZWAbv8jF7nVkNHc9Z5bjHiZVd_RyvjbNukYCYFl_wMGg69_JE6l3rH6zncigBowf2hFQ8CahryY_-VVfF7i8__F3bJenr6ENZClH-PaSpmZf205m5lpcsfNB1U3DcAsBAV2PMibfX_r_R_pWGZYhahrXLQFEOUBBBSyksA-cR8GcpBh_hfMvjcNJHPSj_DIPUzIvgyZYmDkXOXXotfDdb1jYdKNa1c-JeMhsdfbaMNMNS6NodeN0zrm970mxJ4zerU6MrBKwkykVTjAqCEAeVTtKIACueZyzU8b75RZbwWXiTIOM67TrK9O8kZOl0avUdXXAjOa72P9ygbVxTXUr4Fx5Rxjn4QbIlLdzHd1cZKDnYu", "widthPx": 4032, "heightPx": 3024, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Sangyeon Cho", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/106833722526947327072", "photoUri": "https://lh